Waves
=====

This project bundles a WebGL FFT ocean simulation (`simulation.js`, `shared.js`,
`waves.js`) derived from publicly circulated WebGL ocean demos that implement
Stockham FFT spectrum updates on the GPU. The implementation lineage is commonly
associated with interactive WebGL ocean experiments built on Jerry Tessendorf's
FFT wave model.

Project-specific work includes SmartAtlantic buoy integration, PHP ERDDAP
proxying, layout consolidation, station polling, and pinchards.is deployment.

